# Fighting Styles
Archery			KEY:Fighting Style ~ Archery				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighting Style.SpecialQuality	DESC:You gain a +2 bonus to attack rolls you make with ranged weapons.
Defense			KEY:Fighting Style ~ Defense				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighting Style.SpecialQuality	DESC:While you are wearing armor, you gain a +1 bonus to AC.
Dueling			KEY:Fighting Style ~ Dueling				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighting Style.SpecialQuality	DESC:When you are wielding a melee weapon in one hand and no other weapons, you gain a +2 bonus to damage rolls with that weapon.
Great Weapon Fighting	KEY:Fighting Style ~ Great Weapon Fighting	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighting Style.SpecialQuality	DESC:When you roll a 1 or 2 on a damage die for an attack you make with a melee weapon that you are wielding with two hands, you can reroll the die and must use the new roll, even if the new roll is a 1 or a 2. The weapon must have the two-handed or versatile property for you to gain this benefit.
Protection			KEY:Fighting Style ~ Protection			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighting Style.SpecialQuality	DESC:When a creature you can see attacks a target other than you that is within 5 feet of you, you can use your reaction to impose disadvantage on the attack roll. You must be wielding a shield.
Two-Weapon Fighting	KEY:Fighting Style ~ Two-Weapon Fighting		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighting Style.SpecialQuality	DESC:When you engage in two-weapon fighting, you can add your ability modifier to the damage of the second attack.
