Feature: Rustic Hospitality	KEY:Folk Hero ~ Rustic Hospitality		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality	DESC:Since you come from the ranks of the common folk, you fit in among them with ease. You can find a place to hide, rest, or recuperate among other commoners, unless you have shown yourself to be a danger to them. They will shield you from the law or anyone else searching for you, though they will not risk their lives for you.

